# Loops

## For - In
Basic Syntax

```
for [item] in [items] {
	code
}
```
`item` 에 `items` 를 하나씩 대입하여 `code` 를 실행한다.

```
for index in 1...4 {
	print("\(index) times 5 is \(index * 5)")
}
```

### Wildcard Pattern

```
for _ in 0...3 {
	print("Hello.")
}
```
```
for chr in "Hello" {
	print(chr)
	print(type(of:chr))
}
```
```
let list = ["Swift". "Programming", "Language"]

for str in list {
	print(str)
}
```
